com.github.nfcforandroid.api

Interface INfaRecord

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    INdefRecord
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRecord, AndroidApplicationRecord, EmptyRecord, ExternalRecord, MimeTypeRecord, NdefRecord, SmartPosterRecord, TextExternalRecord, TextRecord, UnknownRecord, UnsupportedRecord, UriExternalRecord, UriRecord

    public interface INfaRecord
    Author:
    jefBinomed Simple type interface to guaranty the types of record manipulate with the library. If you want to create a new kind of record, you have to implement this interface. Some standards implementations are already present in the nfa-records module.
